pageProduct.name: Swisse Adults Probiotic & Prebiotic Gummies 45 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Probiotic & Prebiotic Gummies are a deliciously convenient way to get 3 Billion CFU of probiotics, plus a prebiotic source of fibre that feeds good bacteria in the gut.

Swisse Probiotic & Prebiotic Gummies are a deliciously convenient way to get 3 Billion CFU of probiotics, plus a prebiotic source of fibre that feeds good bacteria in the gut.

Product Claims: 3 billion probiotics per serve

Size: 45 Pack

Flavour: Great tasting, natural orange flavour.

Serving Size: Chew 2 gummies daily. Do not swallow whole

KEY FEATURES

• 3 Billion good bacteria per serve
• Contains Inulin (from chicory root fibre) a natural prebiotic and source of fibre that feeds gut bacteria
• No added sugar or sweetener
• Great tasting, natural orange flavour

Warnings

Do not use if cap seal is broken.

Ingredients

Ingredients: Chicory root fibre (60%), Water, Stabilisers (Pectin, Agar Agar), Tapioca Starch, Acidity regulators (Citric acid, tri sodium citrate), Bacillus Coagulans Spores (0.59%), Natural orange flavour, Colour (paprika extract), Glazing agent (Carnauba wax)

Contains: No added lactose, gluten, or egg.

Directions

Chew 2 gummies daily. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct heat.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Swisse is a carbon neutral company. Please recycle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
